65669,lobbying.ie/return/65669/vodafone-ireland,Vodafone Ireland,21/01/2021 10:46,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Public policy or programme,Economic Development and Industry,"Engagement to outline Vodafone's ongoing support in the response to the COVID-19 crisis, and a commitment to supporting the recovery of the economy and society; highlighting the opportunities presented by the National Economic Plan and the investment stimulus provided by the review of the National Development Plan to place the importance of digitalisation at its core.","Leo Varadkar|An Tánaiste|Dáil Éireann, the Oireachtas::Orlaigh Quinn|Secretary General|Department of Business, Enterprise and Innovation::David Hegarty|Assistant Secretary|Department of Business, Enterprise and Innovation::Declan Hughes|Assistant Secretary|Department of Business, Enterprise and Innovation::Philip O'Callaghan|Special Advisor|Department of Enterprise, Trade and Employment::Micheál Martin|An Taoiseach|Department of the Taoiseach::Martin Fraser|Secretary General|Department of the Taoiseach::Deirdre Gillane|Chief of Staff|Department of the Taoiseach::Alan Ahearne|Special Adviser|Department of the Taoiseach::Paschal Donohoe|Minister|Department of Finance::Derek Moran|Secretary General|Department of Finance::Ed Brophy|Special Adviser|Department of Finance::Michael McGrath|Minister|Department of Public Expenditure and Reform::Robert Watt|Secretary General|Department of Public Expenditure and Reform::Grant Sweetnam|Special Adviser|Department of Public Expenditure and Reform::Eamon Ryan|Minister|Department of Climate Action, Communication Networks and Transport::Ciarán Ó hÓbáin|Assistant Secretary|Department of Environment, Climate and Communications::John McDonald|Special Adviser|Department of Transport::Kevin Barrett|Special Adviser|Department of Public Expenditure and Reform",To ensure an understanding of Vodafone's commitment to support the economic recovery and the opportunities provided by focusing stimulus toward digitalisation.,Letter was issued via email on December 17th.|Email|1,Anne O'Leary.,No,,False,,False,
