66659,lobbying.ie/return/66659/the-irish-farmers-association---ifa,The Irish Farmers' Association - IFA,20/01/2021 22:29,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Public policy or programme,EU Affairs,Transposition of EU Directive on Unfair Trading Practices (UTPs) in the Food Supply Chain,"Sinead McPhillips|Assistant Secretary|Department of Agriculture, Food and the Marine::Colm Markey|MEP|European Parliament","To seek an update from the Department of Agriculture on the transposition of the EU Directive into Irish law and to seek a conversation on this, as the deadline per the Directive of May 2021 is looming.",|Email|2-5::|Virtual Meeting|1,Elaine Farrell IFA Oireachtas Executive,No,,False,,False,
66660,lobbying.ie/return/66660/the-irish-farmers-association---ifa,The Irish Farmers' Association - IFA,20/01/2021 22:28,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Public policy or programme,Agriculture,Brexit - Consultative Agriculture Committee of Stakeholders,"Charlie McConalogue|Minister|Department of Agriculture, Food and the Marine::Paul Savage|Assistant Secretary|Department of Agriculture, Food and the Marine::Cecil Beamish|Assistant Secretary|Department of Agriculture, Food and the Marine::Martin Heydon|Minister of State|Department of Agriculture, Food and the Marine::Pippa Hackett|Super Junior Minister|Department of Agriculture, Food and the Marine","To engage with the Minister and Department of Agriculture and Foreign Affairs Officials on:::- the importance of securing a zero-tariff, zero-quota EU/UK trade deal;::- ensuring full respect for the Northern Ireland protocol, and::- on the preparedness for Brexit in the agriculture and food sector",|Virtual Meeting|2-5,"Bryan Barry IFA Deputy Director General, Elaine Farrell IFA Oireachtas Executive, Tadhg Buckley IFA Policy Director",No,,False,,False,
