66756,lobbying.ie/return/66756/the-irish-farmers-association---ifa,The Irish Farmers' Association - IFA,20/01/2021 22:14,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Matters involving public funds,Agriculture,Stakeholder Communication from the Food and Drinks Industry,Micheál Martin|An Taoiseach|Department of the Taoiseach,"That with the COVID-19 restrications, there would be recognitation from the Government towards the Food and Drinks Sector to keep the food chain flowing and open.::To ensure that the approach by Government protects our health but also enables an experienced economy to operate.",|Letter|2-5,Tim Cullinan IFA President,No,,False,,False,
