66808,lobbying.ie/return/66808/irish-exporters-association,Irish Exporters Association,21/01/2021 15:16,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Public policy or programme,Trade,Workers will need training in the issues arising from Brexit including customs,"Charlie McConalogue|Minister|Department of Agriculture, Food and the Marine::Paul Savage|Assistant Secretary|Department of Agriculture, Food and the Marine",Government to assess the need to roll out further Brexit preparedness training,"Took place during a meeting of the Department of Agriculture, Food and the Marine's Brexit Stakeholders forum.|Virtual Meeting|1",Simon McKeever,No,,False,,False,
