nad::Thomas Gould|TD|Dáil Éireann, the Oireachtas","Restoration of the distance coding and increasing Rural Practice Allowances to pre-2009 levels::Funding for additional services – nutrition, counselling etc.::Funding of transport for those receiving addiction counselling or other services::Pilot project for First Aid Overdose and Drug related – 100% funding through Skillnet for training",|Email|2-5::|Virtual Meeting|1,"Thomas Duffy, National President; Denis Duggan, CEO; Derrie Dillon, Head of Advocacy, Membership & Policy, Sean Wallace, Munster Vice-President; Shane Quigley, Rural Youth Chair & Gillian Richardson, Ag Policy Officer",No,,False,,False,
