D|Dáil Éireann, the Oireachtas::Róisín Garvey|Senator|Seanad",Increases to the Just Transition Fund – allowing for the use of Micro-loan scheme to incentivise investment on farm for energy generation and conversion of business.::Significant changes to Retrofit Scheme – Ringfenced rural investment ▪ Reduce barriers to grant – income band reform ▪ Community Energy Grant – expanding ▪ Linking of property tax to energy rating,|Email|2-5::|Virtual Meeting|1,"Thomas Duffy, National President; Denis Duggan, CEO; Derrie Dillon, Head of Advocacy, Membership & Policy, Sean Wallace, Munster Vice-President; Shane Fitzgerald, Ag Affairs Chair & Gillian Richardson, Ag Policy Officer",No,,False,,False,
