67981,lobbying.ie/return/67981/an-taisce-the-national-trust-for-ireland,An Taisce The National Trust for Ireland,20/01/2021 16:32,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Legislation,Taxation,TSG recommendations,Micheál Martin|An Taoiseach|Department of the Taoiseach,"That national climate action and public health interests prevail and the most progressive taxation recommendation of the TSG should be adopted in the forthcoming budget, as well as an equalisation of petrol and diesel taxation and the removal of the farm diesel subsidy.::That the Climate Action and Low Carbon Development (Amendment) Bill 2020 be amended to contain an explicit provision that ensures that new cars and vans sold after 2030 emit no tailpipe emissions.",|Letter|1,Gary Freemantle,No,,False,,False,
