68044,lobbying.ie/return/68044/the-wheel,The Wheel,21/01/2021 14:30,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Public policy or programme,Budgetary matters,"We contacted a number of TD's to ask for them to receive a hard copy of our budget submission and take a photo with it, which they did, between the 16th September and 6th October:","Gary Gannon|TD|Dáil Éireann, the Oireachtas::Jim O'Callaghan|TD|Dáil Éireann, the Oireachtas::Neale Richmond|TD|Dáil Éireann, the Oireachtas::Malcolm Noonan|Minister of State|Department of Housing, Local Government and Heritage::Paul Donnelly|TD|Dáil Éireann, the Oireachtas::Seán Sherlock|TD|Dáil Éireann, the Oireachtas::Joan Collins|TD|Dáil Éireann, the Oireachtas","TD's to take a photo with The Wheel's Pre-Budget Submission, which they did, between the 16th September and 6th October","We contacted a number of TD's to ask for them to receive a hard copy of our budget submission and take a photo with it, which they did, between the 16th September and 6th October

