68300,lobbying.ie/return/68300/pinergy,Pinergy,21/01/2021 10:56,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Legislation,Energy and Natural Resources,Infrastructural & interim plans for micro-generation by SMEs and domestic energy customers. We are concerned about the current plans to roll out how homes & businesses will be able to sell excess electricity to the Grid.,"Eamon Ryan|Minister|Department of Climate Action, Communication Networks and Transport",We would like to see the 'interim' solution up to 2025 replaced with a longer term solution that would enable suppliers to buy in a fair manner excess electricity from their customers.,|Letter|1,Enda Gunnell,No,,False,,False,
