68497,lobbying.ie/return/68497/sse-plc,SSE plc,21/01/2021 15:26,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Zoning or development,Energy and Natural Resources,Consultation Response.,Tom Enright|Chief Executive Officer|Wexford County Council,"Outline the need for Wexford's County Development plan to support the development of both onshore and offshore wind, noting SSE's Arklow Bank projects is close to north Wexford. SSE also wanted to outline that SSE's Great Island Power Station will continue to provide a valuable system service over the coming decades, which SSE recommended  be reflected in the plan.",|Submission|1,John Young.,No,,False,,False,
