68542,lobbying.ie/return/68542/an-post,An Post,21/01/2021 14:50,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Public policy or programme,Communications,"In light of a potential withdrawl of Ulster Bank from the Irish banking market, to highlight An Post's financial services and willingness to be part of any solution that may be under consideration by the Dept of Finance to help facilitate further competition in the market and in particular leverage An Post's franchise and relationships with SME's across Ireland",Des Carville|Head of Unit|Department of Finance,An Post to be  part of any solution that may be under consideration by the Dept of Fin to help facilitate further competition in the market and in particular leverage An Post's franchise and relationships with SME's across Ireland,|Letter|1,David McRedmond Chief Executive An Post,No,,False,,False,
