68544,lobbying.ie/return/68544/sse-plc,SSE plc,21/01/2021 15:21,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Public policy or programme,Energy and Natural Resources,Email providing information on SSE’s sponsorship of COP26.,"Micheál Martin|An Taoiseach|Department of the Taoiseach::Leo Varadkar|An Tánaiste|Dáil Éireann, the Oireachtas::Simon Coveney|Minister|Department of Foreign Affairs::Eamon Ryan|Minister|Department of Climate Action, Communication Networks and Transport::Peter Burke|Minister of State|Department of Housing, Local Government and Heritage::Stephen Donnelly|Minister|Department of Health::Mark Griffin|Secretary General|Department of Environment, Climate and Communications::Matthew Collins|Assistant Secretary|Department of Environment, Climate and Communications","To provide information on SSE's recently-announced sponsorship of the 2021 United Nations Climate Change Conference, COP26, to be held in Glasgow in November 2021, and outline our ambition that the conference will be an opportunity to showcase Ireland’s achievements on Climate Action.  To provide recipients with a copy of the SSE Ireland’s Greenprint for Economic Recovery, much of which can be progressed ahead of COP26.",|Email|1,Stephen Wheeler,No,,False,,False,
