68548,lobbying.ie/return/68548/irish-pharmacy-union,Irish Pharmacy Union,21/01/2021 14:53,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Legislation,Health,Meeting with Minister for Health,Stephen Donnelly|Minister|Department of Health,A meeting with the Minister to discuss expanding the role of pharmacists and to establish a timeframe to commence talks on a new pharmacy contract.,"At the meeting the following issues were discussed:
