68553,lobbying.ie/return/68553/sse-plc,SSE plc,21/01/2021 15:19,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Public policy or programme,Energy and Natural Resources,Covid 19 vaccination rollout plan.,"Matthew Collins|Assistant Secretary|Department of Environment, Climate and Communications","Ensure that rollout plan for COVID-19 vaccination considers priority for vaccine for electricity sector workers who are critical for maintaining security of supply.  This cohort of workers have specialist skills, must work on site and are difficult to substitute if ill, isolating or restricting movements. In combination with thorough COVID-19 site procedures, vaccination will mitigate the risk of security of supply challenges.",|Email|1,Marian Troy,No,,False,,False,
