68558,lobbying.ie/return/68558/charities-institute-ireland,Charities Institute Ireland,21/01/2021 14:57,"1 Sep, 2020 to 31 Dec, 2020",Matters involving public funds,Public Expenditure and Reform,"Regarding the threatened closure of Benefacts, the public platform for financial, governance and regulatory data on all non-profits",Michael McGrath|Minister|Department of Public Expenditure and Reform::Joe O'Brien|Minister of State|Department of Rural and Community Development,"On behalf of our members, we urge an early and a positive resolution to the winding down of Benefacts. At a time when the sector is so needed by society, access to transparent and independent data and insights to support our charitable missions is vital.",|Email|1,Liz Hughes,No,,False,,False,
